curl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/master/scripts/get-helm-3 | bash

helm version --short

Helm will be installed in the below location 

/usr/local/bin/helm


minikube also installed in the below location 
 
/usr/local/bin/minikube

or 

Download location : https://github.com/helm/helm/releases

1.Download your desired release using wget command 

wget https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.7.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz

2.Extract using tar command 

tar -xzvf helm-v3.7.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz

3.Find the helm binary in the unpacked directory, and move it to its desired destination

mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm



